oai_dc:dc.dc:title: ESTIMATION OP WAVE OVERTOPPING QUANTITY OVER SEA-WALLS
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Takada, Akira
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: overtopping
estimation of overtopping
sea walls
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This paper tried to formulate the wave overtopping quantity by using a model of overtopping mechanism. Namely, the author investigated the problem by applying the "Calculation method for discharge of overflow weirs" i.e. the method of Fukui et al.'(1963) and Shi-igai et al. (1970)2).
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 14 (1974): Proceedings of 14th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Copenhagen, Denmark, 1974.; 116
